    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">No crime is too despicable for Gaedren Lamm and his thugs&mdash;a gang of lowlife murderers, kidnappers, and drug dealers that operate in Korvosa&rsquo;s Midland district. You&rsquo;ve lost someone to Lamm and now you&rsquo;re out for revenge.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">While Lamm remains alive and free, you are not slain until your hit point total reaches a negative number equal to your Constitution score + 3. Once Lamm is imprisoned or killed, you lose the former benefit but gain 3 permanent hit points.</span></p>",
